  <title>leg:year <lnpid>id-ST03-26651</lnpid></title>
  <body>
    <section>
     <p>The source context and target mapping of <sourcexml>leg:year</sourcexml> varies by LBU:
      <ol>
       <li><b>For AUSTRALIA:</b> <sourcexml>leg:info/leg:year</sourcexml> becomes <targetxml>primlawinfo:primlawinfo/primlawinfo:dates/primlawinfo:enactdate</targetxml> with attribute <targetxml>@year</targetxml>
        <note><sourcexml>leg:year</sourcexml> input PCDATA transforms only to target attribute <targetxml>primlawinfo:enactdate[@year]</targetxml> and there should be no PCDATA in output.</note>
        <note>For handling <b>@ln.user-displayed</b> attribute, refer the general markup <xref href="../../common_newest/Rosetta_leg.year_ln.user-displayed.dita">ln.user_displayed="false"</xref> section in the CI.</note>
       </li>
       <li><b>For New Zeland:</b> <sourcexml>leg:info/leg:year</sourcexml> becomes <targetxml>primlawinfo:primlawinfo/primlawinfo:dates/primlawinfo:assentdate</targetxml> with attribute <targetxml>@year</targetxml>
       </li>
       <li><b>For UK:</b> <sourcexml>leg:officialnum/leg:year</sourcexml> becomes <targetxml>primlawinfo:identifier/primlawinfo:identifier-component/@type="year"</targetxml></li>
      </ol>
      
     </p>
    </section>
    <example>
      <title>AUSTRALIA SOURCE XML 1: Mapping of <sourcexml>leg:year</sourcexml></title>
      <codeblock>

&lt;leg:year searchtype="LEGISLATION" ln.user-displayed="false"&gt;1970&lt;/leg:year&gt;

      </codeblock>
      <b>Becomes</b>
     <title>AUSTRALIA TARGET XML 1: Mapping of <sourcexml>leg:year</sourcexml></title>
      <codeblock>

&lt;primlawinfo:primlawinfo&gt;
 &lt;primlawinfo:dates&gt;
  &lt;primlawinfo:enactdate year="1970"/&gt;
 &lt;/primlawinfo:dates&gt;
&lt;/primlawinfo:primlawinfo&gt;

      </codeblock>
    </example>
   <example>
    <title>New Zeland SOURCE XML 2: Mapping of <sourcexml>leg:year</sourcexml></title>
    <codeblock>

&lt;leg:year searchtype="LEGISLATION"&gt;1999&lt;/leg:year&gt;

      </codeblock>
    <b>Becomes</b>
    <title>New Zeland TARGET XML 2: Mapping of <sourcexml>leg:year</sourcexml></title>
    <codeblock>

&lt;primlawinfo:primlawinfo&gt;
 &lt;primlawinfo:dates&gt;
  &lt;primlawinfo:assentdate year="1999"&gt;1999&lt;/primlawinfo:assentdate&gt;
 &lt;/primlawinfo:dates&gt;
&lt;/primlawinfo:primlawinfo&gt;

      </codeblock>
   </example>
   <example>
    <title>UK SOURCE XML 3: Mapping of <sourcexml>leg:year</sourcexml></title>
    <codeblock>

&lt;leg:info subseqdoc="false"&gt;
 &lt;!-- ETC. --&gt;
 &lt;leg:officialnum&gt;&lt;leg:year&gt;1236&lt;/leg:year&gt; CHAPTER &lt;leg:seriesnum&gt;4&lt;/leg:seriesnum&gt;&lt;/leg:officialnum&gt;
 &lt;!-- ETC. --&gt;
&lt;/leg:info&gt;

      </codeblock>
    <b>Becomes</b>
    <title>UK TARGET XML 3: Mapping of <sourcexml>leg:year</sourcexml></title>
    <codeblock>

&lt;primlawinfo:primlawinfo&gt;
 &lt;!-- ETC. --&gt;
 &lt;primlawinfo:identifier idtype="officialnum"&gt;
  &lt;primlawinfo:identifier-component type="year"&gt;1236&lt;/primlawinfo:identifier-component&gt; CHAPTER
  &lt;primlawinfo:identifier-component type="seriesnum"&gt;4&lt;/primlawinfo:identifier-component&gt;
 &lt;/primlawinfo:identifier&gt;
 &lt;!-- ETC. --&gt;
&lt;/primlawinfo:primlawinfo&gt;
      </codeblock>
